    p Messagebar Svelte component represents Framework7's <a href="../docs/messagebar.html">Messagebar</a> component.
    h2 Messagebar Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li `Messagebar` - main messagebar element
      li `MessagebarSheet` - messagebar sheet element
      li `MessagebarSheetImage` - messagebar sheet image item
      li `MessagebarSheetItem` - messagebar sheet item
      li `MessagebarAttachments` - messagebar attachments element
      li `MessagebarAttachment` - single messagebar attachment element
